.description
A memory resident "pop-up" program for maintaining a list of names,
addresses and phone numbers, or other flat file database applications.  Can
print labels in up to four columns, to PostScript printers, or any
preferences supported printer. Up to two phone numbers can be stored with
each entry, and dialed automatically using pulse or tone dialing.  Unique
sorting feature allows the user to specify the sort key of each record.
Addresses can be imported and exported via the clipboard, or output using
the unique 'type' feature.  Notes can also be associated with each entry,
using your favorite editor.  Has full ARexx support.  
